{"tid":1758480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銷售員6.16涉推跌六旬漢致死 要繼續還押到下年","createTime":"2019-11-27T05:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T08:00:56.000Z","uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c2de594187ebe90144c5ad7c7609695fa89f98c8","tid":1758480,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"反送中抗爭初期，200萬人於6月16日參與大遊行。當晚人潮散去期間，一名時裝店銷售員被指在中環碼頭與六旬漢爭執，其間推跌對方，令六旬漢兩天後死亡，被控謀殺罪。案件數度提堂，今在東區裁判法院再訊。控方表示要再向毒理化驗官取得死者死因，以進一步諮詢法律意見，申請將案再押後至明年1月8日再訊，獲裁判官批准。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告梁清言（26歲）於今年6月16日在中環7號碼頭外謀殺周鎮和（63歲），導致周在同月18日死亡。案件上次提堂後，押後待控方取得驗屍報告。辯方今指本案已第三次押後，控方應有足夠時間處理案件，為對被告公平起見，要求法庭聲明這是最後一次押後。惟裁判官表示，有見案情嚴重性及複雜性，拒絕辯方要求。被告繼續還柙。"},{"pid":"5df24a55f6927cd5cfd9f39398787b3cb84ff8cf","tid":1758480,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191127/60314665?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191127%2F60314665%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=9e3fa58f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191127%2F60314665%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=9b29abca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191127/60314665?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有險可守?<br />\n全部都紅官黎仆佢個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"